---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Fungi Consultant - Events" currentPage="/events">
  <div class="events-content">
    <h1 class="page-heading">Upcoming Events</h1>

    <!-- Event 1: Open Foundation Talk -->
    <div class="featured-event">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feralchill/fungi/main/IMG_6205.jpeg" class="event-image" alt="Functional Mushrooms: Ecological Allies">

      <h2 class="event-title">Functional Mushrooms: Ecological Allies for Whole-Body Health</h2>
      <p class="event-date">Wednesday 18th February 2026, online via Zoom</p>

      <div class="event-cta">
        <a href="https://open-foundation.org/events/online/functional-mushrooms-ecological-allies-for-whole-body-health/" target="_blank" class="event-link">Sign up or book a space with the Open Foundation →</a>
      </div>

      <input type="checkbox" id="event1Toggle" class="event-toggle">
      <label for="event1Toggle" class="event-expand-link">
        <span class="expand-text">more about this event</span>
        <span class="expand-chevron"></span>
      </label>

      <div class="event-description">
        <p>This talk explores functional mushrooms not simply as supplements, but as ecological allies – organisms with a long history of traditional use and a growing body of scientific research behind them.</p>

        <p>Drawing on insights from immunology, neurobiology, gut microbiome research, and emerging conversations around adaptogens and nootropics, this session invites us to view the body as a living network of relationships — one that can be supported through resilience, balance, and prevention rather than reaction alone.</p>

        <p>This online talk is for anyone curious about mushrooms, interested in integrative health, or looking for new ways to support wellbeing; offering a grounded and thoughtful perspective on working with nature to support the body as a whole.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Event 2: Biohacking Course -->
    <div class="featured-event">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feralchill/fungi/main/IMG_6035.jpeg" class="event-image" alt="Biohacking with Mushrooms Course">

      <h2 class="event-title">Biohacking with Mushrooms: 5-Week Course</h2>
      <h3 class="event-subtitle">Navigating the Science, Benefits & Uses of Functional Mushrooms</h3>
      <p class="event-date">Thursday 5th March 2026</p>

      <div class="event-cta">
        <a href="https://dandelion.events/e/r1d4r" target="_blank" class="event-link">Book tickets and see course outline →</a>
      </div>

      <input type="checkbox" id="event2Toggle" class="event-toggle">
      <label for="event2Toggle" class="event-expand-link">
        <span class="expand-text">more about this event</span>
        <span class="expand-chevron"></span>
      </label>

      <div class="event-description">
        <p>This five-week online course offers a grounded, accessible, and evidence-informed introduction to functional mushrooms, blending modern science, traditional wisdom, and real-world application. Designed for beginners and the curious alike, the course explores how medicinal mushrooms can support cognition, stress resilience, immunity, and overall well-being – without hype or unrealistic promises.</p>

        <p>Each session includes a deep dive into specific mushrooms, practical guidance on sourcing and use, and extended Q&A to help participants apply what they learn to their own lives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Image -->
    <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feralchill/fungi/main/IMG_6018.png" class="bottom-image" alt="">

    <!-- Finish Section -->
    <div class="finish-container">
      <div class="finish-text">
        <span class="brand-name">The Fungi Consultant</span> est. 2024
      </div>
      <div class="footer-text-small">
        <a href="https://anthosponda.art" target="_blank" class="finish-link">site summoned by ælfryth</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Literata:wght@400;500&family=Abril+Fatface&display=swap');

.events-content {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 20px;
}

.page-heading {
  font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif;
  font-size: 2.5em;
  color: #b6c2a0;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 40px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

.featured-event {
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}

.event-image {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 600px;
  height: auto;
  margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 2px solid #e0e0d8;
}

.event-title {
  font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif;
  font-size: 2em;
  color: #63596a;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.event-date {
  font-family: 'Literata', serif;
  font-size: 1.1em;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(82, 81, 92, 0.7);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.event-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Literata', serif;
  font-size: 1.2em;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #52515c;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* Event Toggle */
.event-toggle {
  position: absolute;
  opacity: 0;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
}

.event-expand-link {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 15px 0 0 0;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.expand-text {
  font-family: 'Literata', serif;
  font-size: 1em;
  color: #9a89a4;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  padding-bottom: 2px;
}

.expand-chevron {
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  border-left: 6px solid transparent;
  border-right: 6px solid transparent;
  border-top: 7px solid #9a89a4;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.event-expand-link:hover .expand-text {
  border-bottom-color: #9a89a4;
}

/* When expanded */
.event-toggle:checked + .event-expand-link .expand-text {
  border-bottom-color: #9a89a4;
}

.event-toggle:checked + .event-expand-link .expand-chevron {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
}

/* Description hidden by default */
.event-description {
  background-color: #f9f9f7;
  border: 2px solid #e0e0d8;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 30px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0;
  padding: 0 30px;
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}

/* Show description when toggled */
.event-toggle:checked ~ .event-description {
  max-height: 1000px;
  opacity: 1;
  padding: 30px;
}

.event-description p {
  font-family: 'Literata', serif;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: 1em;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #52515c;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.event-description p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.event-cta {
  text-align: center;
}

.event-link {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif;
  font-size: 2.2em;
  color: #b6c2a0;
  text-decoration: underline;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
  padding: 10px 0;
}

.event-link:hover {
  color: #9a89a4;
}

.bottom-image {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 400px;
  height: auto;
  margin: 60px auto 0 auto;
  display: block;
}

.finish-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0px auto;
  margin-bottom: 0px auto;
  padding: 10px;
  text-align: center;
}

.finish-text {
  font-family: 'Literata', serif;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.8em;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #52515c;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.finish-text .brand-name {
  font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif;
}

.brand-name {
  font-family: 'Abril Fatface', serif;
  font-style: normal;
}

.finish-link {
  color: #b6c2a0;
  font-family: 'Almendra Display', serif;
  font-size: 1em;
  font-weight: bold;
  opacity: 1;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.finish-link:hover {
  color: #4e625c;
  font-weight: bold;
  opacity: 1;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.finish-link:active {
  color: #9a89a4;
  font-weight: bold;
  opacity: 1;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.finish-link:visited {
  color: #b6c2a0;
  font-weight: bold;
  opacity: 1;
}

.footer-text-small {
  font-family: 'Almendra Display', serif;
  font-size: 0.7em;
  color: #b6c2a0;
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .events-content {
    padding: 0 15px;
  }

  .page-heading {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .event-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .event-title {
    font-size: 1.6em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .event-date {
    font-size: 1em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .event-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .event-divider {
    margin: 40px auto;
  }

  .event-description {
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .event-toggle:checked ~ .event-description {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .event-description p {
    font-size: 0.95em;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .event-link {
    font-size: 1em;
  }

  .expand-text {
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  .bottom-image {
    max-width: 200px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
}
</style>
